where to next, friendo?
go from left side of parrott to the frog in a kind of circle motion

cross over the alligator's back and go to gray rocks near giraffe

Go down to the snake
aight, i see the snake now

voila! i've found the treasure. *finished*

good job

head towards the florist stand
ok

cool

nice, i arrived
awesome! now, go a few steps south, between the bench and the wooden branch
you see that green bush? head straight for it
ok, done
nice, just go left between the branch and the bush
ok
just a little further to the east and you should be looking at a cute little deer

ok
spot that medium rock? go along it, then swerve to the right when you see the shark
ok

take a right before hitting the water, duck under that nifty red kayak

and
